{"tid":1547550,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"奶共髮型屋","createTime":"2019-09-06T16:49:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T07:23:38.000Z","uid":93828,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"75e4761e8345416d196363e1cb3fbfeeb215f4a2","tid":1547550,"uid":93828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:49:04.000Z","msg":"是咁的，大家睇住呀，呢間係grand hyatt既<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">BRUNEBLONDE</span></span>髮型屋勁垃圾，兩個法國洋腸總監由六月開始就話反送中既人係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">垃圾</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">死左</span></span>都<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔抵幫</span></span>，要軍隊鎮壓就岩架啦，又話係法國一早就派軍隊<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">打L死班示威者</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，又話d人收左錢示威遊行，成日係度破壞香港。<br />\n是關係因為大家係灣仔遊行個時<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">阻住佢地開舖</span></span>，無錢搵就日屌夜屌。日日就係度同佢d客發表佢d<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">廢藍絲撐黑警偉倫</span></span>。間野已經收到勁貴，整又整得唔靚，兩個老細又仆街，唔比人有其他政見架<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">逆佢地政見者亡</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。睇唔過眼要屌9呢間奶共髮型屋，快Ld執柒左佢啦！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好幫襯呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>屌。<br />\n利申：我的朋友不是我<br />\n兩條法國洋腸<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">背後老細</span></span>係周*馳前女友 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">于x鳳</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/07/001326_63fd98c1c1db775851cfa71f6859064a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F07%2F001326_63fd98c1c1db775851cfa71f6859064a.png&h=b04d4078&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/07/001328_e245aaac443e8baa46361541ecddf8e4.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F07%2F001328_e245aaac443e8baa46361541ecddf8e4.jpeg&h=a2eda7c1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/07/001330_8d9ddbaa62bdcf46d0561dcbf39de1da.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F07%2F001330_8d9ddbaa62bdcf46d0561dcbf39de1da.jpeg&h=121b8d8c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/07/001332_3b399068f24ee08c7f84ca171d3515a7.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F07%2F001332_3b399068f24ee08c7f84ca171d3515a7.jpeg&h=fe3e8d3a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53d52587689c5007b5e309dc3392d6670db0f793","tid":1547550,"uid":110208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:32:57.000Z","msg":"又多間髮型屋blacklist<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59159f96379384e6d8f5b427c53eee9986642892","tid":1547550,"uid":116146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:36:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e15caa64a1c0a53df6316d65c1a34e17be755d81","tid":1547550,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:47:17.000Z","msg":"連登班窮撚撚有錢去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"065bb1bf80346af03a34e798bc1360f584a66ab9","tid":1547550,"uid":61447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:23:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}